      "python is a high level object       oriented dynamically typed interpreted scripting      language as   well as programming languagereadable and simple python emphasizes code readability and uses indentation whitespace to structure blocks of code rather than brackets which many other languages useinterpreted and dynamic it is an interpreted language meaning code is executed linebyline this allows developers to quickly spot errors and test softwarevariables are also dynamically typed so you dont need to specify their data type when writing the codemassive ecosystem python features an extensive batteriesincluded standard library and is supported by a massive ecosystem of thirdparty frameworks and libraries\n"
